  "html": "<h2 class=\"\" id=\"morningradio\">MorningRadio</h2>\n<p class=\"\">Designed to be a healthy \"first screen\" in the morning. News summaries, updates, and enough information about the latest events that you don't feel the need to endlessly doomscroll.</p>\n<p class=\"\">The goal was to repurpose the tik-tok style endless vertical scroll but instead fill it with interesting and useful websites, tools, and news articles (populated through my Pinboard bookmarks)</p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"NOAA notice announcing permanent decommissioning of NOAA-18 satellite on June 6, 2025 due to transmitter failure, with transition guidance to JPSS satellites.\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1755098720/screenshot_2025-08-13_at_11.25.04_AM.png\" alt=\"NOAA notice announcing permanent decommissioning of NOAA-18 satellite on June 6, 2025 due to transmitter failure, with transition guidance to JPSS satellites.\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/v1755098720/screenshot_2025-08-13_at_11.25.04_AM.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/v1755098720/screenshot_2025-08-13_at_11.25.04_AM.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1755098720/screenshot_2025-08-13_at_11.25.04_AM.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/v1755098720/screenshot_2025-08-13_at_11.25.04_AM.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"NOAA notice announcing permanent decommissioning of NOAA-18 satellite on June 6, 2025 due to transmitter failure, with transition guidance to JPSS satellites.\" width=\"978\" height=\"2086\" style=\"--splay-rot:-0.9deg;\" data-dimensions=\"978×2086\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">NOAA notice announcing permanent decommissioning of NOAA-18 satellite on June 6, 2025 due to transmitter failure, with transition guidance to JPSS satellites.</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"\">I even experimented (unsuccessfully) with creating a home screen widget.</p>\n<p class=\"\"><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1749668160/Screenshot_2025-06-11_at_2.55.49_PM.png\" alt=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/v1749668160/Screenshot_2025-06-11_at_2.55.49_PM.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/v1749668160/Screenshot_2025-06-11_at_2.55.49_PM.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/v1749668160/Screenshot_2025-06-11_at_2.55.49_PM.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1749668160/Screenshot_2025-06-11_at_2.55.49_PM.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/v1749668160/Screenshot_2025-06-11_at_2.55.49_PM.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" width=\"1136\" height=\"2168\" style=\"--splay-rot:-0.6deg;\" data-dimensions=\"1136×2168\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></p>",
